        <section id="research">
            <h1>Research</h1>
            <p>My research interests include algebraic combinatorics, cluster algebras, and Schubert calculus. I have been working on various projects related to these areas, aiming to contribute to the understanding and development of combinatorial structures and their applications.</p>
        </section>
